Score-board
===========

A Sailfish application to store scores from games (or not).

It automatically saves previous boards, and they can be modified
later. It allows to create boards up to ten players or teams and
can display the summation of all scores.

Roadmap
-------
* add categories (user editable) to sort boards.
* add templates for games with a specific number of rows (like
  Seven Wonders for instance) and colourise rows.
* add a search functionality in the board history
* ...

